                              Part III. Narrative

     State below in reasonable detail the reasons why Form 10-K, 11-K, 20-F, 
10-Q, N-SAR or the transition report portion thereof could not be filed within 
the prescribed time period. (Attach extra sheets if needed.)
<PAGE>   2
     The Form 10-K for the period ending December 31, 1995 could not be filed 
within the prescribed time period due to the fact that the President and Chief 
Executive Officer, Christopher K. Seglem required surgery on March 20, 1996 and 
has not been able to review the Form 10-K.

                           Part IV. Other Information

     (1)  Name and telephone number of person to contact in regard to this 
notification
                   Robert J. Jaeger          (719) 442-2600
